songs.title: Found
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
Somebody find a waiter
Our lips are dry
Another round for the table
Hold the ice
Pardon me 'cause I'm staring
Oh my god
I can marry that smile you're wearing
And I just might

[Chorus]
Wow
Look at us right now
Finally we're found, found, found, found, found
Run
Go ahead and run around
See how quick you're found, found, found, found, found

[Verse 2]
Sophisticated California
The kids gotta grow
This kinda life is bound to bore you
Yeah, I should know
But you always seem to break the rhythm
Of this messed up world
And there's no way that I'm ever leaving
Without you girl and...

[Chorus]
Wow
Look at us right now
Finally we're found, found, found, found, found (finally)
Run
Go ahead and run around
See how quick you're found, found, found, found, found

[Bridge]
Tell me you want me to love you
Tell me you'll never stopped
I'll be around yeah you're never lost

[Chorus]
Wow
Look at us right now
Finally we're found, found, found, found, found
Baby, you should run
Go ahead and run around
And see how quick you're found, found, found, found, found, yeah
